commit.message: [github-actions] Update build workflow to use newer versions of download-artifact, checkout, and upload-artifact actions
Update NEWS for release
Updated README
Update soversion for release

inotify: Avoid leaking file descriptor to child processes

inotify_init creates a file descriptor which by default is not makes
with CLOEXEC. If the application using libusbmuxd spawns applications
this then leaks through.
Use return value from socket_send instead of using errno
iproxy: Use updated socket_create API to listen on IPv4 and IPv6 with a single socket
Add libusbmuxd_version() function to interface
Move USBMUXD_API to public headers
[github-actions] Update checkout and upload-artifacts to v3

iproxy: Fix typo in log messages

Thanks to @p0358 for reporting.
Remove unneeded buffer copy in device_info_from_plist()
autoconf: Small update to configure.ac
git-version-gen: Prevent multiple lines of output
Add cast to prevent sign-compare compiler warning

autoconf: Fix clang-16 breakage

-Wint-conversion becomes an error by default in clang-16, causing the
program_invocation_short_name test to fail.

Bug: https://bugs.gentoo.org/893910
Allow using libusbmuxd as submodule
[github-actions] Add a scheduled build every 1st of the month so we always have an artifact

Make conn_data member of usbmuxd_device_info struct unsigned since it's not a string

Also remove some pointless casts and update some others
Updated README
automake: Add git-version-gen to EXTRA_DIST and add .tarball-version hook
[github-actions] Windows: Prevent -dirty suffix in version string by disabling CRLF conversion

autoconf: Automatically derive version number from latest git tag

with a fallback to get the version string from a .tarball-version file

Fix typo in comment

Thanks to @timgates42 for pointing this out.
[github-actions] macOS: build for arm64 too
Add build status badge to README.md
[github-actions] Add build workflow
Updated pkg-config file with libimobiledevice-glue dependency
Remove common code in favor of new libimobiledevice-glue
Update deprecated autoconf macros and update m4 files
